---
const title = "Side Software Co";
const description = "Affordable, production-grade software through AI-accelerated delivery. Cloud-native geospatial specialty.";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --text: #1a1a2e;
        --text-muted: #4a4a6a;
        --bg: #fafafa;
        --accent: #2563eb;
        --accent-hover: #1d4ed8;
        --border: #e2e8f0;
        --card-bg: #ffffff;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background: var(--bg);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }

      header {
        padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      header p {
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      section {
        padding: 2.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      section:last-of-type {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .services {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.25rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .service {
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--card-bg);
      }

      .service h3 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .service p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .stack-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .stack-list li {
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-hover);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 2rem 0;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        header {
          padding: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
        }
        header h1 {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        section {
          padding: 2rem 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Side Software Co</h1>
        <p>
          Affordable, production-grade software. We deliver outcomes that used to
          take a full engineering team, powered by disciplined AI workflows and
          DevOps automation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>What we build</h2>
        <div class="services">
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Geospatial systems</h3>
            <p>
              Interactive web maps, spatial APIs, and data pipelines built on OGC
              standards. We deliver the database, the API, the viewer, and the
              infrastructure as a managed bundle.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Custom software</h3>
            <p>
              Websites, internal tools, and data architecture for businesses that
              need something off-the-shelf can't provide. Modern stack, built to
              last.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>AI workflow consulting</h3>
            <p>
              We help engineering teams adopt AI-accelerated development with
              reusable skills, automated verification, and structured agent
              orchestration.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <p>
          The "affordable" part isn't about cutting corners. It's about an
          opinionated operating model that combines AI tooling with open-source
          foundations and DevOps discipline, so a small team ships what used to
          require a large one.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our geospatial work builds on
          <a href="https://github.com/ogc-maps">ogc-maps</a>, an open-source
          organization we maintain with reusable mapping libraries built around
          OGC API standards. Customers pay for delivery and support, not R&D.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Stack</h2>
        <p>Cloud-native, standards-based, and built for maintainability.</p>
        <ul class="stack-list">
          <li>React</li>
          <li>Astro</li>
          <li>PostgreSQL</li>
          <li>PostGIS</li>
          <li>OGC APIs</li>
          <li>MapLibre</li>
          <li>Terraform</li>
          <li>AWS / GCP</li>
          <li>STAC</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          Interested in working together? Reach out at
          <a href="mailto:christopher.esterlein@gmail.com"
            >christopher.esterlein@gmail.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>Side Software Co</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
